cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
title: "nyc-snap-eval: A statute-grounded evaluation suite for caseworker-facing SNAP benefits-navigation AI"
abstract: >-
  An illustrative evaluation suite of approximately seventy test cases across
  seven failure surfaces, anchored to federal (7 CFR Part 273) and state (NYS
  OTDA SNAP Source Book) policy citations, with a published Claude-graded
  rubric and a narrow reference implementation. Scoped to caseworker-facing
  deployment for SNAP in New York at a stated point in time.
